{
    "publish_date": "2012-12-04T16:02:07.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT4M34S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "What do Harry Potter,", 
            "dur": "1.423", 
            "start": "13.988"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Katniss Everdeen, and Frodo", 
            "dur": "2.119", 
            "start": "15.435"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "all have in common\nwith the heroes of ancient myths?", 
            "dur": "2.839", 
            "start": "17.578"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Roar)", 
            "dur": "1.001", 
            "start": "20.441"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What if I told you they are all variants\nof the same hero?", 
            "dur": "2.958", 
            "start": "21.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Do you believe that?", 
            "dur": "1.589", 
            "start": "25.788"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Joseph Campbell did.", 
            "dur": "1.557", 
            "start": "27.401"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He studied myths from all over the world\nand published a book called", 
            "dur": "3.53", 
            "start": "28.982"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;The Hero with a Thousand Faces,&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.097", 
            "start": "32.537"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "retelling dozens of stories", 
            "dur": "1.638", 
            "start": "34.658"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and explaining how each\nrepresents the mono-myth,", 
            "dur": "2.735", 
            "start": "36.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or Hero&#39;s Journey.", 
            "dur": "1.591", 
            "start": "39.079"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, what is the &quot;hero&#39;s journey&quot;?", 
            "dur": "2.606", 
            "start": "42.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Think of it as a cycle.", 
            "dur": "1.144", 
            "start": "44.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The journey begins and ends\nin a hero&#39;s ordinary world,", 
            "dur": "3.662", 
            "start": "46.851"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but the quest passes\nthrough an unfamiliar, special world.", 
            "dur": "4.6", 
            "start": "50.537"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Along the way, there are some key events.", 
            "dur": "2.417", 
            "start": "55.161"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Think about your favorite book or movie.", 
            "dur": "2.587", 
            "start": "57.602"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Does it follow this pattern?", 
            "dur": "1.393", 
            "start": "60.213"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Status quo, that&#39;s where we start.", 
            "dur": "2.033", 
            "start": "63.464"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "1:00: Call to Adventure.", 
            "dur": "2.383", 
            "start": "67.148"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The hero receives a mysterious message.", 
            "dur": "2.526", 
            "start": "69.555"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "An invitation, a challenge?", 
            "dur": "1.654", 
            "start": "72.105"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "2:00: Assistance", 
            "dur": "1.825", 
            "start": "74.572"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The hero needs some help,\nprobably from someone older, wiser.", 
            "dur": "4.677", 
            "start": "76.421"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "3:00: Departure", 
            "dur": "1.56", 
            "start": "81.122"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The hero crosses the threshold\nfrom his normal, safe home,", 
            "dur": "3.357", 
            "start": "82.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and enters the special\nworld and adventure.", 
            "dur": "2.967", 
            "start": "86.087"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;re not in Kansas anymore.", 
            "dur": "1.793", 
            "start": "89.078"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "4:00: Trials", 
            "dur": "1.88", 
            "start": "90.895"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Being a hero is hard work:", 
            "dur": "1.278", 
            "start": "92.799"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "our hero solves a riddle,", 
            "dur": "1.23", 
            "start": "94.101"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "slays a monster,", 
            "dur": "1.219", 
            "start": "95.355"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "escapes from a trap.", 
            "dur": "1.835", 
            "start": "96.598"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "5:00: Approach", 
            "dur": "2.228", 
            "start": "99.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s time to face the biggest ordeal,\nthe hero&#39;s worst fear.", 
            "dur": "3.892", 
            "start": "101.548"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Roar)", 
            "dur": "1", 
            "start": "106.268"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "6:00: Crisis", 
            "dur": "1.49", 
            "start": "108.318"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is the hero&#39;s darkest hour.", 
            "dur": "1.934", 
            "start": "110.843"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He faces death and possibly even dies,", 
            "dur": "2.849", 
            "start": "112.801"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "only to be reborn.", 
            "dur": "1.782", 
            "start": "115.674"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "7:00: Treasure", 
            "dur": "1.798", 
            "start": "118.764"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Roar)", 
            "dur": "1", 
            "start": "120.798"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As a result, the hero\nclaims some treasure,", 
            "dur": "3.645", 
            "start": "122.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "special recognition, or power.", 
            "dur": "1.435", 
            "start": "125.865"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "8:00: Result", 
            "dur": "1.702", 
            "start": "128.251"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This can vary between stories.", 
            "dur": "2.22", 
            "start": "129.977"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Do the monsters bow down before the hero,", 
            "dur": "2.171", 
            "start": "132.221"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or do they chase him as he flees\nfrom the special world?", 
            "dur": "3.907", 
            "start": "134.416"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "9:00: Return", 
            "dur": "1.503", 
            "start": "138.347"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After all that adventure,\nthe hero returns to his ordinary world.", 
            "dur": "3.085", 
            "start": "140.663"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "10:00: New Life", 
            "dur": "2.025", 
            "start": "145.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This quest has changed the hero;\nhe has outgrown his old life.", 
            "dur": "3.913", 
            "start": "147.169"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "11:00: Resolution", 
            "dur": "2.278", 
            "start": "152.318"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All the tangled plot lines\nget straightened out.", 
            "dur": "2.422", 
            "start": "154.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "12:00: Status Quo,", 
            "dur": "2.285", 
            "start": "158.284"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but upgraded to a new level.", 
            "dur": "2.163", 
            "start": "160.593"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Nothing is quite the same\nonce you are a hero.", 
            "dur": "2.216", 
            "start": "162.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Many popular books and movies", 
            "dur": "1.661", 
            "start": "165.784"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "follow this ancient\nformula pretty closely.", 
            "dur": "2.684", 
            "start": "167.469"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But let&#39;s see how well &quot;The Hunger Games&quot;\nfits the hero&#39;s journey template.", 
            "dur": "3.71", 
            "start": "170.177"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When does Katniss Everdeen\nhear her call to adventure", 
            "dur": "2.524", 
            "start": "173.911"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that gets the story moving?", 
            "dur": "1.443", 
            "start": "176.459"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When her sister&#39;s name\nis called from the lottery.", 
            "dur": "2.381", 
            "start": "177.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "How about assistance?", 
            "dur": "1.615", 
            "start": "181.459"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is anyone going to help\nher on her adventure?", 
            "dur": "2.34", 
            "start": "183.098"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Haymitch.", 
            "dur": "1.249", 
            "start": "185.462"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What about departure?", 
            "dur": "1.548", 
            "start": "186.735"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Does she leave her ordinary world?", 
            "dur": "2.097", 
            "start": "188.307"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She gets on a train to the capital.", 
            "dur": "2.193", 
            "start": "190.428"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "OK, so you get the idea.", 
            "dur": "1.425", 
            "start": "192.645"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What do you have in common\nwith Harry Potter,", 
            "dur": "2.428", 
            "start": "194.094"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Katniss Everdeen, and Frodo?", 
            "dur": "1.952", 
            "start": "196.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, you&#39;re human, just like them.", 
            "dur": "2.063", 
            "start": "198.522"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The Hero&#39;s Journey myth\nexists in all human cultures", 
            "dur": "2.892", 
            "start": "201.981"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and keeps getting updated,", 
            "dur": "1.685", 
            "start": "204.897"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because we humans reflect on our world", 
            "dur": "2.262", 
            "start": "206.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "through symbolic stories of our own lives.", 
            "dur": "2.919", 
            "start": "208.892"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You leave your comfort zone,", 
            "dur": "1.973", 
            "start": "213.082"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "have an experience that transforms you,", 
            "dur": "2.455", 
            "start": "215.079"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and then you recover and do it again.", 
            "dur": "1.919", 
            "start": "217.558"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You don&#39;t literally slay\ndragons or fight Voldemort,", 
            "dur": "2.981", 
            "start": "220.459"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but you face problems just as scary.", 
            "dur": "2.538", 
            "start": "223.464"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Joseph Campbell said,", 
            "dur": "1.193", 
            "start": "226.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;In the cave you fear to enter\nlies the treasure you seek.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.717", 
            "start": "227.243"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What is the symbolic\ncave you fear to enter?", 
            "dur": "2.944", 
            "start": "232.143"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Auditions for the school play?", 
            "dur": "1.603", 
            "start": "235.111"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Baseball tryouts?", 
            "dur": "1.72", 
            "start": "237.522"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Love?", 
            "dur": "1.523", 
            "start": "239.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Watch for this formula in books,\nmovies, and TV shows you come across.", 
            "dur": "3.827", 
            "start": "240.813"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You will certainly see it again.", 
            "dur": "1.721", 
            "start": "244.664"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But also be sensitive\nto it in your own life.", 
            "dur": "2.323", 
            "start": "246.409"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Listen for your call to adventure.", 
            "dur": "1.658", 
            "start": "249.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Accept the challenge.", 
            "dur": "1.558", 
            "start": "252.083"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Conquer your fear\nand claim the treasure you seek.", 
            "dur": "2.745", 
            "start": "253.665"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then,", 
            "dur": "1.276", 
            "start": "257.293"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "do it all over again.", 
            "dur": "1.39", 
            "start": "258.593"
        }
    ], 
